    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIRCAL\n20 0020000\n100088500802®\nAIRCAL",
      "AIRCAL\nAirCal's fleet of Boeing 737 aircraft carry 119\npassengers at approximately 550 mph. Normal\ncruising altitude is 28,000 feet. The aircraft\nis powered by two Pratt and Whitney JT-8D\nfanjet engines producing 14,000 pounds of\nthrust each. Maximum takeoff weight is 100,000\npounds. AirCal jets serve major regional air-\nports in the West.\n2015.166.0015"
    ],
